==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stipitate
<hw>Stip"i*tate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[NL.
<ets>stipitatus</ets>, from L. <ets>stipes</ets>, gen.
<ets>stipitis</ets>, a stock. See <er>Stipe</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Supported by a stipe; elevated on a stipe, as the
fronds of most ferns, or the pod of certain cruciferous
plants.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stipitiform</ent>⟦br⟧
